Groups & Private Events
Groups and Private Events
Welcome to Madison Manor House, your premier destination for private corporate events and party rentals. We offer three stunning venue spaces that are sure to impress your guests.
First up is our VIP Lounge, a sophisticated and exclusive space ideal for board meetings, corporate receptions, or intimate gatherings. With a private bar and an intimate atmosphere, it sets the perfect backdrop for networking or celebrating your company's successes.
Next is our Manor House Ballroom, a spacious and versatile venue that is perfect for parties, baby showers, or corporate meetings. Featuring an impressive 80" wall-mounted TV, this space is perfect for presentations or showcasing important content to your attendees.
For an intimate and flexible setting, our Garden Room is the perfect choice. Whether you're planning a bridal shower, birthday party, or a small-scale business meeting, this room offers versatility and a charming ambiance that will make your event truly memorable.
At Madison Manor House, we pride ourselves in providing exceptional service and a variety of beautiful spaces to suit any occasion. Contact us today to book your private corporate event or party rental and let us help you create an unforgettable experience. Call us today at 888-79MANOR or email us at
Events@madisonmanorhouse.com
